e that the project gets shut down.',8,88),(414,'Our Waterybeverage detector is not the cause of any such tremors, or technical malfunctions! Ensure that the project stays up and running, and provide proof showing the project\'s innocence.',5,88),(415,'We believe the loud noises is caused by circuits being overflooded, there should be an open area to build some more generators at ##ZON##-##SUB-1##.',6,88),(416,'The time of using old power methods to power the city has to end! Build a new nuclear power station at ##ZON##-##SUB-1##.',7,88),(417,'The weather is calm outside! No rain, no bad weather, nothing! We have a feeling Internal Security is going to try and shift this onto us, so shift all blame off onto CPU, or Tech Services citing faulty sensor installation.',1,88),(418,'We have word that some shipments that were being sent to us got stuck outdoors, recover theses packages my any means.',4,88),(419,'The shipment sent from another sector was sent in error, we canceled it however the delivery transport was ambushed before it could go back. Ensure that the wreckage is never discovered, and that we arent blamed for anything going wrong!',2,88),(420,'We must show footage of our complex fixing and ending the commie threat! Get footage before the end of todaycycle.',3,88),(421,'The Brain And Reality Neuraliser Engaging Yowler bot is one of our top secret projects, but don\'t let anyone else know! Recover it intact.',7,89),(422,'There\'s word of a powerful propaganda device ont he loose. Capture it intact for us.',3,89),(423,'Whatever is causing the loyalty index to fall so badly would be a powerful tool against enemy complexes. Capture it intact for us.',1,89),(424,'JonArb-U-CLE keeps changing the channel when we\'re getting comfy! Hide all the remote controls for bots and functions in the complex, since he can\'t work the dial!',3,90),(425,'We\'re sick and tired of having to get up and change the channel! Everything should be remote controlled, as soon as possible, so O clearance and below dont have to work as hard! ',6,90),(426,'I hate going to the vet, just so JohnArb-U-CLE can chat up those sexy doctors! Im sure the other citizens feel the same, so make sure no doctors come poking around! ',7,90),(427,'Our recliner chairs keep running out of juice, and its those dumb clone banks and medical centres at fault! Get the doctors and cloners out doing some real work, instead of using all our power! ',6,90),(428,'We\'re the only service group not infected, but we cant let any of the other service groups know. Keep us and our teams quarantined until it\'s cured.',2,90),(429,'Without Od-I-IIE, Nerm-O-LLL and JonArb-U-CLE around, who\'s gonna make us lasagne? Keep them alive at all costs!',1,90),(430,'We\'re the kings of the Sunday Funnies! Publically execute Od-I-IIE, Nerm-O-LLL and JonArb-U-CLE, so were the real stars!',8,90),(431,'Publically terminate Od-I-IIE and Nerm-O-LLL, but keep JonArb-U-CLE alive. That lasagne isn\'t going to make itself.',9,90),(432,'The citizens are crying out for fresh lasagne, but we\'re out of milk and wheat. Find substitutes and cook 30,000 tons of lasagne for the complex.',4,90),(433,'We need more troubleshooter recruits. Ensure we get another 500 volunteers by the end of the daycycle.',9,NULL),(434,'Our troubleshooters aren\'t getting enough public exposure. Ensure a mission is completed successfully in a very public and crowded area.',9,NULL),(435,'So uh... we\'ve been too successful on missions lately. Ensure there\'s at least three failed troubleshooter missions todaycycle, that could reasonably be completed. Otherwise we get zapped for suspected mutant infiltration.',9,NULL),(436,'We need funding, which means stealing from other groups. Ensure our teams get into somewhere with expensive stuff as part of a mission.',9,NULL),(437,'The new clones are working really well together - it must be a secret society plot. Lock down the clone tanks, and make sure we don\'t suffer massive casualties this daycycle so they can\'t increase their numbers.',5,91),(438,'Teela-O\'s ratings are dropping! It must be because we haven\'t done anything big this weekcycle, find a real enemy for her to fight!',3,91),(439,'The new clones are working too well together - it must be a secret society plot! Find an excuse to raid the offices of CPU and HPD&MC, to get evidence of their treason!',8,91),(440,'We\'re not turning out approvals for jackboots fast enough, we think clones are slacking off and faking their work. Get them back to work on the stuff that matters, or get someone outside of CPU to take care of it.',2,91),(441,'Our forces don\'t have enough jackboots, and can\'t fight! Find out who\'s responsible for keeping them from us, and get them terminated!',1,91),(442,'We\'re overstocked on jackboots, find some way of selling them off and making a profit this weekcycle. ',4,91),(443,'AF takes all the good jackboots, and leaves our Troubleshooters with sore feet! Get a replacement manufactured for our clones!',9,91),(444,'PA121-C4N is a brand new chemical we\'re sure will have tremendous benefits for the complex, if we ever figure out what it does. Find out where it went missing, then get Bob-R-OSS to demonstrate it live on his new show!',7,91),(445,'The PA121-C4N is some kind of experimental social lubricant, according to our spies in other service groups. Get us all the existing prototypes, so we can oil the transbot tracks with it.',6,91),(446,'Our loyalty jingles haven\'t been the best. We need this song creator captured to create new glorious recruitment anthems.',1,92),(447,'We cannot delete treasonous files off the torrenting network fast enough! Find a way to disable citizen\'s ability to torrent files!',2,92),(448,'The song is unbelievably catchy... capture the song creator, and we can make him create wonderful new jingles for Alpha Complex!',3,92),(449,'The commie song writer must die, find and eliminate him. Don\'t let Armed Forces muscle in.',8,92),(450,'We need to conserve of power. Ensure power usage is lowered by the end of the daycycle.',6,92),(451,'It\'s not filesharing, it\'s torrenting! Easy distribution of approved materials! Expand it to cover more of the sector and get more seeders, ensure it stays online so the nodes can get in sync.',4,92),(452,'We have a program that can detect all treason on the network, and moves it to our blockchain network! Get it installed onto the systems todaycycle.',7,92),(453,'We are fixing up the network, it may go in and out every now and then. Don\'t get blamed for any networking issues.',5,92),(454,'We need something to show how efficient we are. Have troubleshooters bring in the GREEN Giggle Gang!',9,93),(455,'We\'re running out of raw resources for paper. Reduce the need for paper by 15%.',4,93),(456,'INFRAREDs are at an all time happiness high! Ensure it stays this way.',3,93),(457,'We have an experimental paper replacement in the works, but to implement it requires a need. Increase the need for paper by 15%.',7,93),(458,'We\'re only just passing quotas for automated alerts this week. Make sure none of our new keywords get taken out of the rotation.',2,94),(459,'Our identification and termination rates for high clearance citizens has been off the charts this past weekcycle, and the Computer has been singing our praises. Make sure we keep up the good work.',8,94),(460,'The proles in this sector are absolutely incompetent! They can\'t even operate a simple food vat. Get us some more high clearance citizens working on producing food.',4,94),(461,'User testing on the latest model of the food vats was... less than thorough, and they\'re too complex for the average clone to use. Make sure this doesn\'t come back to bite us.',5,94),(462,'The proles in this sector are absolutely incompetent! Luckily we\'ve just managed to acquire a big group of high clearance citizens to work the power plants and keep the lights on in the sector. Make sure we don\'t lose them!',6,94),(463,'Power Services are in