rwork. Ensure Work Order ##SUB-FLAV## gets implemented without any amendments or riders.',2,96),(477,'Sherl-O-CKH is making a mockery of us. Embarrass them pubicly.',8,97),(478,'We need someone like Sherl-O-CKH with us, they\'ll make our success rate go through the roof. Recruit them willingly into the Troubleshooters.',9,97),(479,'Sherl-O-CKH is driving the indicies crazy with his reckless antics. Return the indicies to nominal levels.',2,97),(480,'Ensure Sherl-O-CKH doesn\'t end up investigating any of our troops.',1,97),(481,'Don\'t let Sherl-O-CKH near any of our experiments, he embarasses anyone he touches.',7,97),(482,'Get Sherl-O-CKH on camera, solving crimes alongside Armed Forces or R&D! It\'ll be a smash hit!',3,97),(483,'It\'s been monthcycles since any of our experimental toys got approved! Get one of our experimental toys in circulation as a toy by the end of the daycycle. Our \"Sea Monkey\" project is a good candidate',7,98),(484,'We\'ve been completely swamped in paperwork from other service groups. Luckily a few daycycles worth have \"disappeared\" from our queue, so we\'re nearly on schedule. Make sure this doesn\'t come back to bite us.',2,98),(485,'Citizens are hungrier than ever. If they keep eating at this rate we\'ll be out of food by the end of the weekcycle. Get our food stockpiles back to nominal.',4,98),(486,'Bouncy Bubble Beverage sales are down, we need to remind citizen this drink tastes great! Get 3 teams in service groups you don\'t control to promote the drink in subtle ways.',3,99),(487,'We need some high-clearance ambassadors from our newest arrivals! Promote 5 of our arrivals to Blue or higher.',4,99),(488,'These mutants are going to overrun us! Ensure that we engage them and repel their forces.',1,99),(489,'We need to know how these citizens infiltrated our defences. Interrogate these citizens so we can improve them.',8,99),(490,'We are getting a nice cut of the profits thanks to the markup we charge for \"super-fast\" shipping on