ing to citizens. All citizens must be reminded that large Rogue PetBots have roamed outside Alpha Complex and their cries can be heard through the vents.',3,100),(502,'Our scrubbots assigned to houses in this sector are currently working overtime. With an increased concentration on this area, other locations in this sector are getting filthy. Please ensure that the hygiene index remains above zero.',3,100),(503,'We have received reports that the FiresideChat will not be using our electricity for the show tonight, they are generating it from bicycles instead. They don\'t know what they are doing! Please ensure they connect themselves up.',6,100),(504,'We\'ve been challenged by the Head of Troubleshooters to prove that our Bots in the Kitchen can produce the highest quality cuisine. Present this food onto the Fireside Chat this evening.',5,100),(505,'One of our WarBots stationed in Sector ABA is disrupting communications by continuously broadcasting a \"Requesting Reinforcements\" signal. We have tried doing this, but it has amplified the problem. Remove all the WarBots we sent before we are blamed for this mess.',5,100),(506,'We have received a request for the interview questions for tonight\'s Fireside Chat interview. We have been unable to locate them, please track them down for HDPMC.',2,100),(507,'We are excited that the talk show has been getting low ratings. Ensure that the ratings of tonight episode are below 10,000 so that we can revive Travis\' Tech Talk in that slot going forward, so more citizens learn something constructive.',2,100),(508,'I\'ve made a bet with Head of Tech Services that FC\'s Chosen can cook better than the Bots in the Kitchen. Ensure that the food is served during the Fireside Chat show so our efforts don\'t go to waste.',9,100),(509,'There has been a mixup with the team assignment of a new Red clearance troubleshooter with a registered mutation. Can you slot in Ketchum-R-ASH into your effort todaycycle?',9,100),(510,'We have this huge stock of edible bottles. They taste bad and dissolve in water, but we need them sold. Sell most of them by the end of the daycycle.',4,100),(511,'Those PetBot Vermin are more of a hindrance then a help, they are even making the General\'s boots shake in terror! Send a brigade out to destroy them!',1,101),(512,'We\'ll look extremely competent if we can remove the quarantine this daycycle! Ensure that you remove the quarantine measures, but be sure that no one has any objections to this order.',8,101),(513,'We have developed a potential cure for the virus, but we need citizens with the virus. Get us some so we can test the treatment.',7,101),(514,'IRs need more fresh nappies, but we\'ll need more fabric to achieve this. Collect as many uniforms as you can and deliver them to Nappy Factory ##SUB-101-NAPPY##.',4,101),(515,'Citizens are currently bored inside their houses and are threatening to leave if they cannot be entertained. Develop something that will keep them occupied for a while.',3,101),(516,'A Violet-Clearance Air Conditioner temperature request for Sector DED has been received, please keep the thermostat between 30 to 40 degrees.',6,101),(517,'There is a bug in the cloning template, do not let anyone find out about this.',5,101),(518,'We have taken the DED cloning tanks offline after a secret society attempted to obtain control of the system. Dismantle and transport the cloning tubes to a undisclosed location to discourage the perpetrators.',2,101),(519,'FC has told Dispatch that the new PetBots aren\'t scary at all. Send a team to find some of the PetBots and prove to the public that they are harmless!',9,101),(520,'Somehow we got a work order for harvesting 3 megalitres of sweat and urine from DED citizens. It needs to be filled by the end of the daycycle.',9,101),(521,'Opal-G-OPI has been spotted in this sector. Find him and bring him in so he can be court marshalled for harbouring a unregistered mutation.',1,102),(522,'We have listened to Teela\'s new album and it sucks! Get us access to her private server so we can make it sound more pleasing. Don\'t let HPD&MC know.',2,102),(523,'We need to fulfil our construction contracts, ensure that all current houses in the sector are destroyed so we can build new ones.',3,102),(524,'We need to push Teela\'s new album out today, we have thwarted several attempts to change some of the songs, Teela\'s individuality will not shine through otherwise. Make sure the album releases as intended.',4,102),(525,'We need to keep making these raincoats, but the plastic prices are too expensive. Can you steal some from the Recycling Plant?',5,102),(526,'Sprinklers are going off all over the sector and people are slipping! We need you to dry the floors and make sure we aren\'t blamed for this.',6,102),(527,'We need more waterproofing for our new scrubBot prototypes and the old ones are short-circuiting. The plastic prices are quite steep, so could you take some from the Recycling Plant?',7,102),(528,'If we can\'t find Teela-O then citizens will lose faith in our law enforcement abilities. Find Teela-O and hold a press conference celebrating our success to boost our reputation.',8,102),(529,'Before she went missing, Teela-O wanted one of our Teams to feature in \"I am a Model Citizen\", but the recording was scheduled for later today. Can you ensure we make it into the final mix?',9,102);
